@startuml
skinparam shadowing false

title E2E Flow - Product Ingestion and Hybrid Search

autonumber

actor Client
participant "ProductController" as ProductController
participant "IngestProductUseCase" as IngestProductUseCase
participant "ProductWriteAdapter" as ProductWriteAdapter
participant "ProductIngestionPublisher" as ProductIngestionPublisher
queue "BullMQ Queue" as Queue
participant "ProductIngestionProcessor" as ProductIngestionProcessor

participant "EmbeddingAPIAdapter" as EmbeddingAPIAdapter
database "PostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL
participant "SearchController" as SearchController
participant "SearchProductsUseCase" as SearchProductsUseCase
participant "HybridSearchOrchestrator" as HybridSearchOrchestrator
participant "PostgresFTSAdapter" as PostgresFTSAdapter
participant "PgVectorAdapter" as PgVectorAdapter
participant "RrfService" as RrfService

== Ingestion ==
Client -> ProductController: POST /products
ProductController -> IngestProductUseCase: execute(input)
IngestProductUseCase -> ProductWriteAdapter: createProduct(input)
ProductWriteAdapter -> PostgreSQL: INSERT product
PostgreSQL --> ProductWriteAdapter: product(id)
ProductWriteAdapter --> IngestProductUseCase: product
IngestProductUseCase -> ProductIngestionPublisher: publishProductCreated(event)
ProductIngestionPublisher -> Queue: enqueue ProductCreatedEvent
IngestProductUseCase --> ProductController: product queued
ProductController --> Client: 201 Created

== Async Embedding Worker ==
Queue -> ProductIngestionProcessor: consume ProductCreatedEvent
ProductIngestionProcessor -> EmbeddingAPIAdapter: generateProductEmbedding(text)
EmbeddingAPIAdapter --> ProductIngestionProcessor: embedding vector
ProductIngestionProcessor -> ProductWriteAdapter: updateProductEmbedding(productId, vector)
ProductWriteAdapter -> PostgreSQL: UPDATE embedding
PostgreSQL --> ProductWriteAdapter: ok
ProductWriteAdapter --> ProductIngestionProcessor: ok
ProductIngestionProcessor --> Queue: complete job

== Search ==
Client -> SearchController: GET /search?q=...
SearchController -> SearchProductsUseCase: execute(query)
SearchProductsUseCase -> HybridSearchOrchestrator: search(input)
HybridSearchOrchestrator -> PostgresFTSAdapter: lexicalSearch(query)
PostgresFTSAdapter -> PostgreSQL: FTS query
PostgreSQL --> PostgresFTSAdapter: lexicalResults
PostgresFTSAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: lexicalResults
HybridSearchOrchestrator -> EmbeddingAPIAdapter: generateQueryEmbedding(query)
EmbeddingAPIAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: query vector
HybridSearchOrchestrator -> PgVectorAdapter: vectorSearch(vector)
PgVectorAdapter -> PostgreSQL: pgvector similarity
PostgreSQL --> PgVectorAdapter: semanticResults
PgVectorAdapter --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: semanticResults
HybridSearchOrchestrator -> RrfService: fuse(semantic, lexical)
RrfService --> HybridSearchOrchestrator: fusedResults
HybridSearchOrchestrator --> SearchProductsUseCase: results
SearchProductsUseCase --> SearchController: results
SearchController --> Client: 200 OK

@enduml
